      <item>
        <title>Adding Geolocation post</title>
        <description>&lt;h1 id=&quot;geolocation-post&quot;&gt;Geolocation post&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Today I have written a little script to use the browser’s geolocation features
to report the latitude and longitude of the current position.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The script is a very simple use of the Vue.js framework.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I hope you like it!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
